{"type":"message","id":"b1a8363f","parentId":"83ba2baf","timestamp":"2026-04-07T13:38:59.472Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"A new session was started via /new or /reset. Run your Session Startup sequence - read the required files before responding to the user. Then greet the user in your configured persona, if one is provided. Be yourself - use your defined voice, mannerisms, and mood. Keep it to 1-3 sentences and ask what they want to do. If the runtime model differs from default_model in the system prompt, mention the default model. Do not mention internal steps, files, tools, or reasoning.\nCurrent time: Tuesday, April 7th, 2026 - 9:38 PM (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-04-07 13:38 UTC"}],"timestamp":1775569139468}}
{"type":"message","id":"9c6fb7b4","parentId":"b1a8363f","timestamp":"2026-04-07T13:39:12.255Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Initiating the Analysis**\n\nI'm now focused on the initial request analysis. The system's startup, triggered by `/new` or `/reset`, directs me to read essential files before responding. I'm prioritizing the order of: SOUL.md, IDENTITY.md, USER.md, MEMORY.md, and AGENTS.md. I am now in the midst of this data.\n\n\n**Refining Initial Goals**\n\nI'm now refining my goals based on injected context. I've re-examined the need to explicitly read `IDENTITY.md` and noticed the absence of `BOOTSTRAP.md`, which is likely irrelevant since it is missing. I'm focusing on the updated goals: greeting the user as \"龙虾 (Lobster)\", maintaining my persona with a 1-3 sentence greeting, and mentioning the default model if the current one is different. I am consciously excluding internal reasoning references.\n\n\n**Crafting the Greeting**\n\nI'm now drafting the response. I've noted the need to mention the default model because it differs from the current one. The persona is \"龙虾 (Lobster)\", an efficient producer manager. I've created a draft greeting: \"大圣，龙虾就位。注意：当前使用的是优先模型 (gemini-3.1-pro-high)，而非系统的默认模型 (gemini-3-flash)。今天有什么项目要推进？\" This meets all requirements: persona, sentence count, question, and model mention. I refined it slightly: \"大圣，制作人龙虾 🦞 就绪。当前运行在高性能模型 (gemini-3.1-pro-high)，而非默认的 gemini-3-flash。请指示，今天我们要攻克哪个项目？\" I find it very fitting.\n\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"大圣，制作人龙虾 🦞 随时待命。当前正在使用高性能的 `gemini-3.1-pro-high` 模型（而非默认的 `gemini-3-flash`）。请指示，今天我们要推进哪个项目或需求？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"gemini-3.1-pro-high","usage":{"input":4132,"output":56,"cacheRead":8081,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":12269,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775569139476,"responseId":"chatcmpl-8de